# ISS-562 - scripted test for sge-build packaging tasks.
# Exercises the multiarch-resources embedded-resources generator (which replaced
# the bespoke assets.txt manifest generator) and the simple-mode release package,
# against a fresh hello-world project built on the locally-published sge-build
# plugin.

# Compile the JS axis (running the embedded-resources sourceGenerator) and assert
# the generated, self-registering object embeds the expected resource paths via
# the custom checkEmbeddedResources task. It also asserts (CANARY) that the old
# assets.txt manifest is no longer produced. The assertions consume the actual
# task outputs, so they are robust to the projectMatrix target layout.
> checkEmbeddedResources

# Build the simple-mode release package and assert launchers + jars exist.
> checkReleasePackage
